      "content": "thanks. i'm just a bit nervous about calling the clinic because they charge a lot for follow ups if it's not a big deal. do you think the ointment is enough to kill any bacteria if the redness stays? i don't want to wait 24 hours if it gets worse, i'd rather just fix it now with the cream and a warm cloth. is it safe to just keep doing that until it clears up?",
